about.summary: A cowsay clone for python in one file.

name: cowpy
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "cowpy" %}
{% set version = "1.1.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://github.com/jeffbuttars/cowpy/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: "9bd1c3e1bf87be496484ea2d843f45a3e058bc3c7eeb23d303efb1bf2bd14e85"

build:
  number: 1
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - cowpy

about:
  home: https://github.com/jeffbuttars/cowpy
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: "A cowsay clone for python in one file."

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - carterbox
